{"tid":944670,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想同大家分享一個，關於我夢想既故事","createTime":"2018-12-17T10:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T04:53:31.000Z","uid":68626,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd09cf9531066c49f477d9c3bedbf1a5e9f184d","tid":944670,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:13:03.000Z","msg":"首先多謝你地禁入黎先<br />\n呢個故事可能會有少少長<br />\n其實我由細到大既夢想就係做律師<br />\n但係公開試考得唔好<br />\n之後聽講澳洲考 foundation入當地法律系易過係香港好多<br />\n我亦揾過好多呢方面既資料<br />\n覺得呢個方向都幾岩我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係屋企無錢呀屌你老母<br />\n畢業咪去撚左做跟車囉 唔係點撚樣呀？<br />\n之後？<br />\n之後咪跟撚到依加日日做體力勞動囉<br />\n無錢點撚樣追夢呀<br />\n靠屋企有錢想追乜撚野都得啦<br />\n追個明星仔任屌都仲得呀"},{"pid":"87abbfa3a4dd05fe988dd4880ae7d2e3d0d5b7a9","tid":944670,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"a0827edc41d7cb3a2c55f6fe0c6b1a5e0b6a5e39","tid":944670,"uid":20066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"有錢人追夢係易呀<br />\n但唔代表夢想唔使付出架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4574d8bd35983a2e6bd07480ebb1bbbdc41f41d9","tid":944670,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0827edc41d7cb3a2c55f6fe0c6b1a5e0b6a5e39","tid":944670,"uid":20066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"有錢人追夢係易呀<br />\n但唔代表夢想唔使付出架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"窮撚連追都無得追添"},{"pid":"7e92da2fce227c348e1f0e1751e1a57b5804517f","tid":944670,"uid":20066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4574d8bd35983a2e6bd07480ebb1bbbdc41f41d9","tid":944670,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0827edc41d7cb3a2c55f6fe0c6b1a5e0b6a5e39","tid":944670,"uid":20066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"有錢人追夢係易呀<br />\n但唔代表夢想唔使付出架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/